snippet.title: Figment 2: Creed Valley - Prologue Karaoke Teaser
snippet.description:
The FREE Figment 2: Creed Valley prologue is out now! 

Play now:  https://s.team/a/1502260

Figment 2: Creed Valley is an action-adventure game set in the human mind. Join Dusty, The Mind’s courage, as you make your way through puzzles, musical boss fights and unique environments. Get a taste of this surreal and whimsical adventure in the prologue.
